10152961[=]ustv[=]lazybum[=]2010-03-05 11:01:53[=]这里有美剧翻译吗？[=]我是美国雪城大学（Syracuse University)攻读传媒硕士的，有个不情之请。就是各位美剧翻译能否赏脸让小妹采访一下，讨论关于中美流行文化的现状。 我不是灌水来的，也没有商业企图，完全是为了写论文，论文的目的也是为了推进中美文化交流发展。如果想看论文的proposal，可以发给大家。 如果能够请有兴趣的翻译们联系一下我的话，私下讨论细节，无限感激 我的qq：1409889562 I am a master student from the Newhouse School of Public Communications in Syracuse University, it is a very well-known insitution, and I am 100% legitimate.  I am only looking for volunteers to help me with my study about translation group's contribution to China's popular culture.  I am not looking to make money or to exploit anyone in anyway.  I promise to protect your privacy and not ask sensitive questions.  Please feel free to contact me with any questions, I will be happy to discuss my study with you. Thank you again for taking the time to read my post.
